result.markdown: --- title: "Week 2: Time series graphics" --- ::: {.cell} ::: ## What you will learn this week * Different types of plots for time series including time plots, season plots, subseries plots, lag plots and ACF plots * The difference between seasonal patterns and cyclic patterns in time series * What is "white noise" and how to identify it. ## Exercises (on your own or in tutorial) Complete Exercises 1-5 from [Section 2.10 of the book](https://otexts.com/fpp3/graphics-exercises.html). ## Pre-seminar activities Read [Chapter 2 of the textbook](https://otexts.com/fpp3/graphics.html) and watch all embedded videos ## Assignments * [IA1](../assignments/A1.qmd) is due on Monday 10 March. * [GA1](../assignments/G1.qmd) is due on Monday 24 March.
